** Sterling High School (Houston), named for the governor
* Ross N. Sterling (1931–1988), United States federal judge</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q880965" start="31" end="47" title="Ross S. Sterling" label="Ross S. Sterling"/>
<link wikidata="Q7611419" start="79" end="109" title="Sterling High School (Houston)" label="Sterling High School (Houston)"/>
